To create an apple .dmg package, you need to:

1. Compile QLC
   * cd ..
   * qmake -spec macx-g++ -recursive
   * make

2. Install QLC to the default installation path (~/QLC.app/)
   * make install

3. Run the .dmg creation script in this directory
   * cd create-dmg
   * ./create-qlc-dmg

